NewRefcountedPointees(L, N') := RefcountedPointees(L, N),
PointeesOfPtr(L), NextInteger(N', N), N' != 0
NewRefcountedPointees(L, N)  := RefcountedPointees(L, N), not PointessOfPtr(L)

NextInteger(N', N) maps N' = N-1 to N

To add the pointee set of Ptr to RefcountedPointees(L, N), we can do
the reverse:

NewRefcountedPointees(L, N') := RefcountedPointees(L, N),
PointeesOfPtr(L), NextInteger(N, N')
NewRefcountedPointees(L, 1)  := not RefcountedPointees(L, _), PointessOfPtr(L)
